# Implementation Plan - Rename Pop the Balloon to Punctuation

The goal is to rename the "Pop the Balloon" game to "Punctuation" throughout the application for better clarity and alignment with the game's actual content.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This change involves renaming directories and files. If you have any external bookmarks or links pointing directly to `/games/poptheballoon/`, they will need to be updated to `/games/punctuation/`.

